data.description: Wonderful opportunity to enjoy Shelton Springs, a community of newer homes near Shelton High.  Quality built 2018 single level 3 bedroom/2 bath home by Rexford Homes features plaster 9' ceilings throughout. The primary bath includes a large vanity and a garden tub with separate shower.  Spacious kitchen is adjacent to the laundry/mud room and open to the living room.  All appliances-including laundry pair- stay! Natural gas furnace and water heater, and the living room is anchored by the gas fireplace with wood mantle. Fully finished rear load garage with alley access and near the community park, you'll love this convenient location close to schools and with great Hwy 101 access.
